Package util

The util package contains general purpose, utility java classes for working in the BCID system.

Class Summary
dates Convenience class for working with dates related to bcids.
SettingsManager util.SettingsManager provides a generic way to configure BiSciCol core classes from a properties file.
 

Package util Description

The util package contains general purpose, utility java classes for working in the BCID system. The most important one here is the SettingsManager class. It also contains a dates class for working with date formats in a standard way.
